{{glossary}}
{{term|term= '''[[Schwann cell]]'''}}
{{defn|defn= The principal glia of the [[peripheral nervous system]] (PNS).}}

{{term|term= '''[[Ground tissue#Sclerenchyma|sclerenchyma]]'''}}
{{defn|defn= It is a type of the cell walls which have thick lignified secondary walls and often die when mature.}}

{{term|term= '''[[sexual reproduction]]'''}}
